    CreateOrderFragment
    Creates Create Dashboard of the application Customer can create new orders here
    CustomerDashboard
    Creates Main Dashboard of the application Can switch to different fragments from here
    FragmentAcitivityConstants
    Creates constants for Actiivity fragments
    HomeFragment
    Creates a home fragment to display the order history of a customer.
    Login
    Creates a Login Activity to enable validation for user
    ReadyForPickupFragment
    Creates a fragment to display message to customer when he/she reaches the store

    Creates a fragment to display maps activity with store location
